**Summary:** This documentation covers the `@supertokens-plugins/captcha-react` plugin that provides React integration for CAPTCHA providers (ReCAPTCHAv2, ReCAPTCHAv3, Turnstile) with SuperTokens authentication forms, including component overrides for EmailPassword and Passwordless authentication flows.

